import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { PairingServiceService } from 'src/app/food-wine-pairing/pairing-service.service'; import { IFoodWinePair } from 'src/app/Interfaces/FoodWinePair'; @Component({ selector: 'app-pairing-list', templateUrl: './pairing-list.component.html', styleUrls: ['./pairing-list.component.css'] }) export class PairingListComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private repositoryService: PairingServiceService) {} FoodWinePair: IFoodWinePair | any pairedWines: string[] = [] ngOnIt(): void{ //this.getWines(); console.log("console"); alert("alert") } getWines(){ this.repositoryService.getWinePairing().subscribe( (response) => { alert("test") ; this.FoodWinePair = response; this.pairedWines=this.FoodWinePair.pairedWines; }); } }
